Had our delicious meal by @wokheysg consisting of fragrant egg fried rice with shrimps, Black Pepper Fried rice with Grilled chicken and Ramen with beef delivered right to our doorstep by the lovely @foodpandasg 💗⁣
⁣
So many other local food options available at @foodpandasg so please do support our #localfoodsg ❤️❤️Stay Healthy and Stay Safe guys!⁣
